comments: Bogdanovic (SAC) briefly grasps Davis's (LAL) uniform before releasing.
Davis (LAL) sets the pick in Bogdanovic's (SAC) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Bogdanovic (SAC) makes marginal contact James (LAL) during his shooting motion that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Bogdanovic (SAC) makes marginal contact with Davis (LAL) at the end of the drive.
Hield (SAC) and Caldwell-Pope (LAL) engage and disengage before going over the screen.
Davis (LAL) makes incidental contact with Bogdanovic's (SAC) arm that does not affect his ability to make the pass.
Bogdanovic (SAC) moves laterally into James's (LAL) path and affects his SQBR.
Barnes (SAC) and James (LAL) engage and disengage off ball.
Davis (LAL) sets the pick in Barnes's (SAC) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Barnes (SAC) sets the pick in Caldwell-Pope's (LAL) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Caldwell-Pope (LAL) makes brief tactile contact with Hield's (SAC) body that does not affect his trajectory before Davis (LAL) makes incidental contact with Hield's body during his follow-through.
Caruso (LAL) and Ferrell (SAC) make incidental leg contact during the rebound.
Kuzma (LAL) makes marginal contact with Boganovic's (SAC) body during the driving shot attempt.
James (LAL) makes marginal contact with Barnes's (SAC) front at the start of the drive before both players make incidental leg contact.
James (LAL) extends his elbow into Barnes's (SAC) chin before any contact is initiated by Barnes on the perimeter.
Davis (LAL) does not have his arms in a vertical position, but the contact initiated by Barnes (SAC) occurs to Davis's chest.  Davis then blocks the shot attempt by Barnes.
Holmes (SAC) attempts a take foul on Davis (LAL) but the contact is marginal.
